01:41:56.260 --> 01:41:59.950
you don’t have to pay to the doctors, nothing.

01:41:59.950 --> 01:42:05.030
That’s one thing one should know you can’t
pay for God.

01:42:05.030 --> 01:42:06.030
You can’t.

01:42:06.030 --> 01:42:07.090
God doesn’t understand money.

01:42:07.090 --> 01:42:09.800
He doesn’t understand bank.

01:42:09.800 --> 01:42:16.400
He has no idea about what all these things
we have done to ourselves.

01:42:16.400 --> 01:42:23.540
So best thing is to remember that only you
have to give some respect to your self-realisation.

01:42:23.540 --> 01:42:24.540
Respect yourself.

01:42:24.540 --> 01:42:29.510
Love and compassion for yourself And forgive
yourself.

01:42:29.510 --> 01:42:37.740
That’s one of the ways we can really understand
that we are human beings at the epitome of

01:42:37.740 --> 01:42:41.820
evolution and we have to achieve this in our
lifetime.

01:42:41.820 --> 01:42:48.020
It is such a tremendous luck that at this
time at this juncture you are here.

01:42:48.020 --> 01:42:57.480
To get your realization and grow into it.

01:42:57.480 --> 01:43:12.200
May god bless you!

