So you have to say in your heart – you can
call me Mother or Sri Mataji, Mother I am

01:46:30.500 --> 01:46:33.100
not guilty at all.

01:46:33.100 --> 01:46:42.770
The another simple thing to do is as you have
forgiven yourself forgive everyone.

01:46:42.770 --> 01:46:48.220
Even without thinking about them.

01:46:48.220 --> 01:46:53.460
Because logically whether you have forgiven
or not you have done nothing.

01:46:53.460 --> 01:46:56.070
I don’t forgive means what.

01:46:56.070 --> 01:47:05.740
Means that I am torturing myself all the time
all my life for somebody who is enjoying himself.

01:47:05.740 --> 01:47:12.310
We play into wrong hands if we don’t forgive.

01:47:12.310 --> 01:47:14.210
But by that what happens to our chakras.

01:47:14.210 --> 01:47:23.560
That this centre in the crossing of the optic
chiasm is like this is absolutely constricted.

01:47:23.560 --> 01:47:24.870
Absolutely constricted.

01:47:24.870 --> 01:47:29.680
And unless and until you don’t forgive it
won’t open at all and the Kundalini cannot

01:47:29.680 --> 01:47:30.680
cross over.

01:47:30.680 --> 01:47:34.730
This is the last barrier we have.

01:47:34.730 --> 01:47:42.680
So just forget and forgive all the people
in general if you want.

01:47:42.680 --> 01:47:43.860
Don’t think about them.

01:47:43.860 --> 01:47:48.710
Because that is also a headache to remember
whom you have to forgive.

01:47:48.710 --> 01:47:51.250
They don’t deserve that attention.

01:47:51.250 --> 01:47:57.350
So just forgive altogether, you will feel
lighter even now immediately if you just forgive

01:47:57.350 --> 01:47:58.670
everyone.

01:47:58.670 --> 01:48:02.710
These are the two conditions.

01:48:02.710 --> 01:48:05.110
I don’t think are so difficult.

01:48:05.110 --> 01:48:10.740
Third one is you have to take out your shoes.

01:48:10.740 --> 01:48:18.030
But I hope you don’t mind because in England
first time when I said you have to take out

01:48:18.030 --> 01:48:24.840
your shoes half of them walked out.

01:48:24.840 --> 01:48:28.540
Why shoes because this Mother Earth helps
us a lot.

01:48:28.540 --> 01:48:30.380
She sucks in our problems.

01:48:30.380 --> 01:49:01.210
When you’re your socks on it doesn’t matter.

01:49:01.210 --> 01:49:03.620
Now you know that these five are sympathetic.

01:49:03.620 --> 01:49:24.010
Now you please put these hands towards me
like this.

01:49:24.010 --> 01:49:32.870
Just like this.

01:49:32.870 --> 01:49:48.760
Please put your right hand towards me like
this and the left hand on top of the fontanel

01:49:48.760 --> 01:49:56.550
bone area (tadu) which was the soft bone on
top of your head.

01:49:56.550 --> 01:49:58.420
Now put down your head.

01:49:58.420 --> 01:50:03.230
Now please don’t put it on top.

01:50:03.230 --> 01:50:06.520
But away from it.

01:50:06.520 --> 01:50:08.330
Now see for yourself.

01:50:08.330 --> 01:50:11.900
Please put down your head.

01:50:11.900 --> 01:50:19.840
If you want you can take out your spectacles.

01:50:19.840 --> 01:50:29.450
Now see for yourself if there’s a cool or
hot breeze like vibrations are coming out

01:50:29.450 --> 01:50:33.060
of your fontanel bone area.

01:50:33.060 --> 01:50:35.240
Some people get it a little far away.

01:50:35.240 --> 01:50:37.280
Some get it quite close.

01:50:37.280 --> 01:50:38.640
Now don’t feel guilty.

01:50:38.640 --> 01:50:46.030
I can feel your centres out of which this
guilty business is quite a lot.

01:50:46.030 --> 01:50:52.870
If it is hot then you should know that you
have not forgiven yourself and or you have

01:50:52.870 --> 01:50:54.610
not forgiven others.

01:50:54.610 --> 01:50:57.250
So please forgive now.

01:50:57.250 --> 01:50:58.430
You can move your hand.

01:50:58.430 --> 01:51:00.520
It may be close to your head.

01:51:00.520 --> 01:51:02.310
It might be away from it.

01:51:02.310 --> 01:51:03.310
Depends on.

01:51:03.310 --> 01:51:07.860
And move your hand and see for yourself.

01:51:07.860 --> 01:51:10.840
Now please put left hand towards me.

01:51:10.840 --> 01:51:21.140
And please put down your head and see for
yourself on top of your head on the fontanel

01:51:21.140 --> 01:51:25.530
bone area which was the soft bone in your
childhood.

01:51:25.530 --> 01:51:30.490
See for yourself if there is a cool or a hot
breeze coming out of your head.

01:51:30.490 --> 01:51:32.990
Out of your head.

01:51:32.990 --> 01:51:43.200
Here again I will request you to forgive yourself
and to forgive others.

01:51:43.200 --> 01:51:44.370
Please.

01:51:44.370 --> 01:51:49.090
That will definitely help.

01:51:49.090 --> 01:51:50.270
Now.

01:51:50.270 --> 01:51:53.350
Please take your right hand towards me.

01:51:53.350 --> 01:52:00.660
And now see for yourself with your left hand
on top of your head if there’s a cool or

01:52:00.660 --> 01:52:16.030
a hot breeze like vibrations

01:52:16.030 --> 01:52:17.030
are coming.

01:52:17.030 --> 01:52:18.030
Actually, you have to desire it.

01:52:18.030 --> 01:52:21.340
It is not meant for arrogant people.

01:52:21.340 --> 01:52:24.890
But meant for humble who want to have their
self-realisation.

01:52:24.890 --> 01:52:34.490
You have to humble down.

01:52:34.490 --> 01:52:41.920
Now please put both your hands towards the
sky like this and put back your head.

01:52:41.920 --> 01:52:43.150
Push back.

01:52:43.150 --> 01:52:48.750
Here you have to ask a question in your heart
three times.

01:52:48.750 --> 01:52:52.230
Any one of these questions you can ask.

01:52:52.230 --> 01:52:53.230
Three times.

01:52:53.230 --> 01:52:57.290
Mother is this the cool breeze of the Holy
Ghost?

01:52:57.290 --> 01:53:02.130
Or Mother is this the all-pervading power
of Divine Love?

01:53:02.130 --> 01:53:07.810
Or Mother is this the Param Chaitanya?

01:53:07.810 --> 01:53:14.300
Ask any one of these questions three times.

01:53:14.300 --> 01:53:16.730
In your heart.

01:53:16.730 --> 01:53:22.400
Push back your head and your hands.

01:53:22.400 --> 01:53:27.280
Now please take down your hands.

01:53:27.280 --> 01:53:35.620
Now, if you can put both your hands towards
me like this and watch me without thinking.

01:53:35.620 --> 01:53:43.250
Just watch me without thinking.

01:53:43.250 --> 01:53:44.500
Some people are getting it here.

01:53:44.500 --> 01:53:47.930
So you can push it up if they are getting
down here.

01:53:47.930 --> 01:53:52.610
Just push it up.

01:53:52.610 --> 01:54:00.790
Watch me without thinking.

01:54:00.790 --> 01:54:06.960
All those who have felt cool breeze on the
fingertips or in the centre of the palm or

01:54:06.960 --> 01:54:16.460
out of the fontanel bone area, whether hot
or cool, please raise both your hands.

01:54:16.460 --> 01:54:22.360
My goodness!

01:54:22.360 --> 01:54:31.770
I bow to you all of you have felt it which
is very great experience for me.

01:54:31.770 --> 01:54:33.850
So may God bless you all.

01:54:33.850 --> 01:54:37.140
Now your saintly life has started.

01:54:37.140 --> 01:54:39.120
So be careful.

01:54:39.120 --> 01:54:44.450
You don’t have to give up anything outside.

01:54:44.450 --> 01:54:47.930
You don’t have to renounce anything.

01:54:47.930 --> 01:54:54.730
Everything there and you have become a saint.

01:54:54.730 --> 01:55:03.580
So please respect your self-realisation and
develop it so that you can help yourself and

01:55:03.580 --> 01:55:07.280
help everyone around.

01:55:07.280 --> 01:55:14.620
I must tell you I was surprised that there
was a good centre started in Israel.

01:55:14.620 --> 01:55:19.290
And the people who started were Germans and
Austrians.

01:55:19.290 --> 01:55:29.850
IT was such a feeling of joy for me that look
at these Germans they feel responsible for

01:55:29.850 --> 01:55:34.830
the Jews they have gone to Israel to give
them their realisation.

01:55:34.830 --> 01:55:37.650
Such love and such compassion.

01:55:37.650 --> 01:55:44.740
Such transformation that you will enjoy your
virtues you will enjoy yourself.

01:55:44.740 --> 01:55:53.380
May God bless you all.

01:55:53.380 --> 01:55:59.570
I will like our school children to sing one
song so that they will see for themselves

01:55:59.570 --> 01:56:14.280
how they have picked up if there are here.

01:56:14.280 --> 01:56:19.560
Are there our school children here?

01:56:19.560 --> 01:56:22.730
Have we got?

01:56:22.730 --> 01:56:25.890
No not here.

01:56:25.890 --> 01:56:26.950
Any?

01:56:26.950 --> 01:56:30.120
Come here then.

01:56:30.120 --> 01:56:42.800
‘Sabko aane nahi diya shayad’ (Perhaps
they were not allowed to come).

01:56:42.800 --> 01:56:47.020
Yes yes come along.

01:56:47.020 --> 01:56:50.180
Nothing like children.

01:56:50.180 --> 01:56:53.810
We have to learn so much from them.

01:56:53.810 --> 01:56:55.260
Alright.

01:56:55.260 --> 01:56:59.600
Come and join.

01:56:59.600 --> 01:57:02.510
Come forward.

01:57:02.510 --> 01:57:09.460
All the little girls should sit in front.

01:57:09.460 --> 01:57:13.060
And the little boys.

01:57:13.060 --> 01:57:17.560
‘Samne aao’ [Hindi] (come forward).

01:57:17.560 --> 01:57:18.560
Yes.

01:57:18.560 --> 01:57:19.360
Good.
